                <p>Many people in Arizona looked up at the night sky on March 13, 1997, and saw something that would become one of the most talked-about and documented UFO sightings in recent history. What they saw would make them question what they thought they knew about reality, cause a government scandal, and leave questions that are still unanswered almost thirty years later.</p>

